/* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
   STATE
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
let query = '';

/* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
   SEARCH
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
function onSymSearch() {
  query = document.getElementById('symQ').value.trim().toLowerCase();
  render();
}

/* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
   RENDER
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
function render() {
  let filtered = CATS;

  if (query) {
    filtered = filtered.map(cat => {
      const nameMatch = cat.name.toLowerCase().includes(query);
      const syms = nameMatch ? cat.s : cat.s.filter(sym => sym === query || sym.toLowerCase().includes(query));
      return { ...cat, s: syms };
    }).filter(c => c.s.length);
  }

  const total = filtered.reduce((a, c) => a + c.s.length, 0);
  document.getElementById('sCount').textContent = query ? total + ' found' : '';

  // Split the categories into 4 sections so ads fit between them perfectly
  const chunkSize = Math.ceil(filtered.length / 4);
  
  renderContainer('symPart1', filtered.slice(0, chunkSize));
  renderContainer('symPart2', filtered.slice(chunkSize, chunkSize * 2));
  renderContainer('symPart3', filtered.slice(chunkSize * 2, chunkSize * 3));
  renderContainer('symPart4', filtered.slice(chunkSize * 3));
}

function renderContainer(id, cats) {
  const el = document.getElementById(id);
  if (!el) return; // Safety check
  el.innerHTML = '';

  if (!cats.length) {
    // Only show the 'Not Found' message in the very first block
    if (id === 'symPart1' && query) {
      el.innerHTML = `<div style="padding:40px;text-align:center;color:#aaa;background:#fff;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid #dce0e8;margin-bottom:14px;">
        No symbols found for "<strong>${query}</strong>". Try: heart, face, star, arrow, lettersâ€¦
      </div>`;
    }
    return;
  }

  cats.forEach(cat => {
    const block = document.createElement('div');
    block.className = 'sym-block';
    block.id = 'cat-' + cat.id;

    const hd = document.createElement('div');
    hd.className = 'sym-block-hd';
    hd.innerHTML = `<h2>${cat.name}</h2><span class="cnt">${cat.s.length} items</span>`;

    const grid = document.createElement('div');
    grid.className = 'sym-grid';

    cat.s.forEach(sym => {
      const s = document.createElement('div');
      s.className = 'sym';
      s.textContent = sym;
      s.title = 'Click to add: ' + sym;
      s.onclick = () => copySym(sym, s);
      grid.appendChild(s);
    });

    block.appendChild(hd);
    block.appendChild(grid);
    el.appendChild(block);
  });
}

/* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
   COPY BOX LOGIC
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */
function copySym(sym, el) {
  const copyBox = document.getElementById('copyBox');
  
  // 1. Get current cursor position
  const startPos = copyBox.selectionStart;
  const endPos = copyBox.selectionEnd;
  const text = copyBox.value;

  // 2. Slice the text and insert the symbol at the cursor
  copyBox.value = text.substring(0, startPos) + sym + text.substring(endPos);

  // 3. Move the cursor to right after the newly inserted symbol
  const newPos = startPos + sym.length;
  copyBox.setSelectionRange(newPos, newPos);
  
  // 4. Keep the input focused so you don't lose your spot
  copyBox.focus();

  // 5. Visual feedback
  el.classList.add('copied');
  setTimeout(() => el.classList.remove('copied'), 520);
  
  toast('Added to box: ' + sym);
}

function clearBoxText() {
  document.getElementById('copyBox').value = '';
  toast('Box cleared!');
}

function copyBoxText() {
  const box = document.getElementById('copyBox');
  if (!box.value.trim()) {
    toast('Nothing to copy!');
    return;
  }

  navigator.clipboard.writeText(box.value).then(() => {
    toast('Copied to clipboard!');
  }).catch(() => {
    box.select();
    document.execCommand('copy');
    toast('Copied to clipboard!');
  });
}

let _tt;
function toast(msg) {
  const el = document.getElementById('toast');
  el.textContent = msg;
  el.classList.add('show');
  clearTimeout(_tt);
  _tt = setTimeout(() => el.classList.remove('show'), 1800);
}

